channel.title: How do you take off Server control panel without having problems?
channel.description:
I don't like the control panel because when my server auto restarts, it takes to long to close and then for the new one it will say port already in use :S. So I tried moving the CP files outa my server files and then theres a problem with my compiler. Obviously I needed to do something else :S But where :(
Heres what my compiler looks like [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/jv2iab.jpg[/img]

item.title: How do you take off Server control panel without having problems?
item.dc:creator: @ranger_squad ranger squad
item.description:
@ranger_squad wrote:

Open up server.java, [ctrl]+[f] and type in CP CP And delete the line, then [ctrl]+[f] CP(). and delete that line.
